Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.52,0:00:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.48,0:00:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你在的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.91,0:00:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.67,0:00:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小孩竟然把我家的佑...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 在吵什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀 這不是美有樹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.59,0:00:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了呢 怎麼了 這麼早來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 把佑還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑君？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在這裏嗎 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.17,0:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹 難得來一趟 上來坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒有那個空閒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把佑帶出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 美有樹急性子的地方一點都沒變呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.95,0:00:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了 你就上來坐一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.37,0:00:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 拿雙拖鞋出來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.54,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}\N 穿\N \N越 \N \N時 \N \N空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有事要傳達給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什...什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.92,0:02:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙...你一定要保護好遙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為...為什麼我必須要被你說這些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你...就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.90,0:03:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 安靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.04,0:03:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是好久了呢 美有樹到我們家來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去可是一直來玩的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人一起來喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.38,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 在這種時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在這種時候才好喝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 不用客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是很好喝的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.50,0:04:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天要喝個痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說些什麼啊 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這個地方一點都沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 我看上去有那麼年輕麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了慶祝和舊友的再會 來乾杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.88,0:04:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 要去告訴佑才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.12,0:04:27.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒出息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.72,0:04:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得嚇唬小孩子很有趣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.88,0:04:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.62,0:04:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你給我記住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃的話就一定會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不願意輸的話就戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抱有戰鬥的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 怎麼辦啊 被阿姨知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算像這樣一直藏起來 總有一天還是會被找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去管他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙還不會去體會他人的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉是未來的佑的話 告訴他怎麼做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.41,0:05:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是自己去嘗試並克服就沒有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼那樣...太無情了 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的未來？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:55.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙說的話 根本不能相信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.74,0:06:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這沒志氣的樣子算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.74,0:06:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.12,0:06:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有骨氣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.27,0:06:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要以為自己是大人就了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙才不是我的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一點都不瞭解我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 和佑之間發生了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也...也不是什麼了不起的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.48,0:06:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 讓他暫時在我們家裏玩一段時間好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行 那孩子還有考試要參加
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是最重要的時期
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 那種口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是把我當作那種強迫自己小孩參加考試的笨蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從以前開始就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:53.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是把我當笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.37,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼都不和我商量一下就決定了大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大學？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你不是去了東京的美大嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 合格的時候不是好好的和你解釋過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去東京的大學
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐要去早鍛煉 先走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啦 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的姐姐 原本應該去東京的大學的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.02,0:07:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我要代替她...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 媽媽卻不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽一直很喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起一事無成的我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.26,0:07:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我來...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:07:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說我和死去的大阿姨很像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.09,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以努力學習的話 一定能進好的中學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是絕對要考進才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.92,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香 再倒一杯給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是喝的太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 因為真的很好喝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.26,0:08:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑是個非常乖巧的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能成為像惠美姐姐一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香也是這麼認為的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃...是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的佑可以成為像惠美姐那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對 絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部灑出來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我家的鋼琴上還放著照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.95,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那些裏面 有我媽媽中學時候的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和大阿姨一起拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.94,0:09:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經問過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把這個擺出來裝飾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.78,0:09:18.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後媽媽她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠美姐姐他頭腦聰明 運動萬能 什麼都好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:27.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開朗 有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以佑一定可以成為像姐姐那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.40,0:09:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得...有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起哦 明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事啦 我去買酒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽為什麼...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把我和大阿姨做比較呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我見都沒有見過大阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.16,0:10:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 在二年前外婆死了以後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽開始和我說起大阿姨的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們去問一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去問為什麼佑的媽媽要把佑和自己的姐姐做比較
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.61,0:10:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢 去問那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.21,0:10:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.58,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.68,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 要好好的問清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.05,0:10:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.51,0:10:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放手啦 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.30,0:10:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.86,0:10:46.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 我們有事要問您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.16,0:10:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.64,0:10:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點和我一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:10:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不聽你的藉口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 請聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.86,0:11:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 這事和你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要把佑和阿姨的姐姐做比較呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且阿姨你 二年前從來沒有和佑說過那種話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年前？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.30,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 那是從札幌的外婆的葬禮後開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.27,0:11:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會代替姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:44.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.89,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空在歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽她消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.24,0:12:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 遙 你們在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.20,0:12:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個椅子是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.30,0:12:51.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.59,0:12:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.82,0:12:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 媽媽出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:12:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧 美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.31,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝果汁嗎 美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.48,0:13:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不相信我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想離家出走的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是因為相信你 才把你叫到我家來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.84,0:13:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離家出走說起來簡單 可你有好好計畫過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我把存的錢都帶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.52,0:13:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 中學生的...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日香和我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.66,0:13:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.71,0:13:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.82,0:13:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.79,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑的媽媽 消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.32,0:13:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 媽媽消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊 你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與不同的時空接觸了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.75,0:14:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的思想有的時候會給時空帶來影響
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.01,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的思想？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成宇宙中所有物質的量子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.84,0:14:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的思想有時會產生干涉它的力場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.14,0:14:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是最喜歡姐姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦好 又開朗 還那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能代替她死去就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也是認為那樣比較好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可不能這麼想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為比起我...媽媽...更加喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽只一味注視著死去的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都是 比起我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨現在在哪裡啊 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不同的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在擁有她無法忘卻的思念的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念的時空？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.03,0:15:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在過去 在過去的某個時空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是因為我的力量造成這樣的後果的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把她帶回來也是可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要確定她轉移的時空不是一件容易的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.72,0:15:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在無限擴展的時空中尋找一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就如同在沙灘上尋找掉落的一根針一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙的話應該能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候你也改變了時空的流向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.61,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個時候的事情我已經記不太清了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話 一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信它吧 相信自己的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.17,0:16:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不行 不能順利進行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.34,0:16:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己 你一定能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不感受到阿姨的想法就不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉 我去下面試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得要那樣才會更加接近阿姨的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.22,0:17:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 就在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.37,0:17:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.64,0:17:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去感覺就可以了 去感覺阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹如果離家出走的話 伯父伯母一定會很擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.34,0:17:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.61,0:17:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會擔心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的會擔心我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我想成為像姐姐一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像姐姐一樣被周圍人所愛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.29,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想離家出走什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想引起媽媽的注意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.29,0:18:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我沒有離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.22,0:18:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是乘纜車翻過山就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以媽媽 也沒有擔心我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.09,0:18:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能稍微離我遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 讓佑的媽媽回到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是...什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:01.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這...這是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.20,0:20:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.69,0:20:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的美有樹不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅行包也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹在我家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想已經和明日香一起睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子真是的...讓我那麼擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心我嗎 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年 那孩子的姐姐因為交通事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那孩子也不在了的話 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.09,0:21:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 所以就不要太責備她了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 當然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天就做那孩子喜歡的漢堡肉餅等她回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.18,0:21:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.63,0:21:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡漢堡肉餅的是惠美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.70,0:21:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 只要是媽媽親手做的料理都喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.80,0:21:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹已經睡著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.73,0:21:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方睡著的話會感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.55,0:21:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 快起來 美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 把手給我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.67,0:21:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 佑 在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.60,0:21:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個..
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:21:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道已經和你媽媽見過了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.57,0:22:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.95,0:22:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 美有樹 去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.22,0:22:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.82,0:22:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.11,0:22:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.13,0:22:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在沙發上睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.34,0:22:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美有樹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.21,0:22:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.28,0:22:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.33,0:22:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是母子麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽睡著了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽還想再在這裏坐一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想和遙的媽媽再聊一會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.44,0:22:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她是我的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.30,0:22:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.22,0:23:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叛徒...要消滅掉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.12,0:24:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.11,0:24:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏日的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.11,0:24:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,15年後會怎麼樣啊 你說出來看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.40,0:24:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再妨礙我的話 就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.73,0:25:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.93,0:25:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 暴風雨的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.43,0:25:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候能告訴我嗎


